# what is gama-fit?
gamafit is fitness hub centre who is meant to be self-care oriented the app goal is to reach your goals and also support the user in the process 

# why this project 
i always wanted something like this, a app that can support me, if it can support me i hope it will support others that is the reason this repo 

#features overview
- fitness orientation[ sleep,food,workout ] these big three can be tracked 
- analytics and proper data [ eg it will show you your lifts data,weight,muscle focus analysis,pomodoro stats]
- mark logger 
- gama cli 
- themes and database import export
